TITLE: Client-side Random Stock Price Generation Method
DESCRIPTION: Original implementation of the refreshWatchList method that generates random stock prices in the client-side code. This will be replaced with server-side data retrieval.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gwtproject/gwt-site/blob/main/src/main/markdown/doc/latest/tutorial/JSON.md#2025-04-09_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
/**
 * Generate random stock prices.
 */
private void refreshWatchList() {
  final double MAX_PRICE = 100.0; // $100.00
  final double MAX_PRICE_CHANGE = 0.02; // +/- 2%

  StockPrice[] prices = new StockPrice[stocks.size()];
  for (int i = 0; i < stocks.size(); i++) {
    double price = Random.nextDouble() * MAX_PRICE;
    double change = price * MAX_PRICE_CHANGE
        * (Random.nextDouble() * 2.0 - 1.0);

    prices[i] = new StockPrice(stocks.get(i), price, change);
  }

  updateTable(prices);
}
```

