TITLE: Creating a UiBinder Composite Class in GWT
DESCRIPTION: Defines a Main class that extends Composite and implements UiBinder pattern to separate UI code from presentation. This creates the basic structure for the TodoList application's main screen.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gwtproject/gwt-site/blob/main/src/main/markdown/doc/latest/polymer-tutorial/widgets-buildui.md#2025-04-09_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: java
