TITLE: Embedding User Data in the GWT Host Page
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to pass data from the server to GWT code by embedding a JavaScript object in the host page. It creates a 'info' object containing the user's email which can be accessed immediately when the GWT module loads.
