TITLE: Template-Based GWT Host Page Using JSP
DESCRIPTION: This JSP template implements the dynamic host page pattern with cleaner syntax. It checks user authentication and conditionally includes the GWT module script and user data, while also providing appropriate login/logout links.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gwtproject/gwt-site/blob/main/src/main/markdown/articles/dynamic_host_page.md#2025-04-09_snippet_6

