TITLE: Implementing Deferred Command Pattern in GWT
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use DeferredCommand with IncrementalCommand to implement a deferred Iterator pattern. This prevents UI blocking while creating UI elements from a list of data objects.
SOURCE: https://github.com/gwtproject/gwt-site/blob/main/src/main/markdown/articles/gwt-iphone.md#2025-04-09_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
final List objects = ....;
  DeferredCommand.addCommand(new IncrementalCommand() {
    Iterator i = objects.iterator();
    public boolean execute() {
      Foo foo = (Foo)i.next();
      .... do something ...
      return i.hasNext();
    }
  });
```

